    "role": "agent",
    "message": "You're very welcome, Ben! Just to recap, you now have one upcoming appointment tomorrow, November nineteenth at four thirty PM with Dr. Rakesh Kumar, and our front desk team will be reaching out about the billing details. Have a great day!"
