  },
  {
    "role": "agent",
    "message": "Perfect! So the refill is for you, Ben. Now, what medication would you like to refill, and which pharmacy would you like to pick it up from?"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "message": "I want a citrican dihydrochloride two hits and I would like to pick it from Edward Pharmacy in New Jersey."
  },
  {
    "role": "agent",
    "message": "Excellent! I've submitted your refill request for Cetirizine dihydrochloride two tablets to be picked up at Edward Pharmacy in New Jersey. The pharmacy and our clinic will process this..."
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "message": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "role": "agent",
    "message": "You're welcome, Ben! Is there anything else I can..."
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "message": "Okay, sure."
  },
  {
    "role": "agent",
    "message": "Great! What else can I help you with today?"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "message": "I'm good actually. Thanks."
  },
